{"tid":735723,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"機械人鬥快大賽：中國 13 秒 日本 15 秒 香港 40 秒！！！","createTime":"2018-07-09T16:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T19:02:42.000Z","uid":14170,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f4f43d624f84d22399897caabe18ed413edeae","tid":735723,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"中國代表 東北大學：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/a-wkUEHfleg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fa-wkUEHfleg&d=RG0b9rNgKUGB%2BmnGwwe2DqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=17a1f4f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/a-wkUEHfleg</a><br />\n<br />\n日本代表 東京大學：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e_kXcbyrsoU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe_kXcbyrsoU&d=RG0b9rNgKUGB%2BmnGwwe2DqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9b6d4ba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e_kXcbyrsoU</a><br />\n<br />\n香港代表 香港科技大學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比賽玩法：<br />\n<br />\n雙方機械人企對邊，場區分紅藍兩方。<br />\n每邊有兩個機器人，一負責傳球，另一負責投球，投射目標有兩個，分別係低框 &amp; 高框。<br />\n遊戲開始時，傳球機械人負責取球和傳球，而投球機械人需要先在近處射入低框，然後再到遠處射入低框，取得分數。<br />\n射完低框，投球機械人才可到場區中心射高框，以取得更高分數，最後高分者贏得遊戲。<br />\n不過，如果投球機械人成功將球射入高框同時投進圓區，就無視當前分數馬上能夠勝出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738f0ed42cd568d5c18b0a092175edca2fda9882","tid":735723,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9ea2cf59dfa184a9700b8b3791d2482a118eb3","tid":735723,"uid":46588,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"出過國就知香港除左炒樓炒股票外就無野叻<br />\n講it連印度都追唔上"},{"pid":"1667d41cb9f9185ba00d855eb845a9b8d9116633","tid":735723,"uid":43032,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5c9ea2cf59dfa184a9700b8b3791d2482a118eb3","tid":735723,"uid":46588,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"出過國就知香港除左炒樓炒股票外就無野叻<br 